Command palette installed!

Usage:
import { CommandPalette } from '@/components/command-palette/command-palette'

<CommandPalette
  items={[
    { id: '1', label: 'Go to Dashboard', group: 'pages' },
    { id: '2', label: 'Create new project', group: 'actions' },
  ]}
  groups={[
    { id: 'pages', label: 'Pages' },
    { id: 'actions', label: 'Actions' },
  ]}
  onSelect={(item) => router.push(item.id)}
/>

Requires shadcn/ui: npx shadcn@latest add dialog input
